self.assertEqual('Always Sensitive', enums.convert_attribute_tag_to_name(
    enums.Tags.ALWAYS_SENSITIVE))
args = 'invalid',
self.assertRaisesRegex(ValueError,
    'The attribute tag must be a Tags enumeration.', enums.
    convert_attribute_tag_to_name, *args)
args = enums.Tags.COMMON_ATTRIBUTES,
self.assertRaisesRegex(ValueError, 'Unrecognized attribute tag: {}'.format(
    args[0]), enums.convert_attribute_tag_to_name, *args)
